                  </seg>
                  <desc>The word God is not rubricated in the first three works; the word Mary is rubricated in the final two works</desc>
                  <desc>Columetric layout of text: <locus target="#90v #91r"/> (Ps. 129); <locus target="#97v"/> (Ps. 150); <locus target="#104v"/> (ninth Biblical Canticle); <locus target="#104v #105r"/> (tenth Biblical Canticle).</desc>
