                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d1"><locus target="#iv(erso)"/><desc> crude drawing of a figure</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d2"><locus target="#76r"/><desc> crude drawing of a talismanic symbol</desc></decoNote>
                    <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d3"><locus target="#120v"/><desc> top: picture of a priest with prayer stick and sistrum with caption <q>“Zion;”</q> Underneath him is a person carrying the ark surrounded by two figures with arms upstretched and holding something over the ark. To the left is an image of <desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1066DavidHarp"/>, with the caption, <q>“As David the prophet prayed, I will pray to you, God, my creator”</q> (an excerpt from God Reigns). Bottom center is a miniature of <desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="AT1031VirginAndChild"/> with the two archangels on either side.  To the lower left is an <ref type="authFile" corresp ="AT1012Equestrian"/> , presumably Saint George</desc></decoNote>
