                      <loucs target="#13v #20v #29v #36r #67r #86r #93v #98r #118r #121r #122r #125v"/> (multiple full stops between lines of alternating red and black dots).
                    </decoNote>
                  </decoDesc>
                  <additions>
                  <list>
                    <item xml:id="a1">
                    <desc type="Asmat">
                    <locus target="#125v"/>: Asmat prayer for help in writing,  <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸሎት፡ በእንተ፡ ምሥጢረ፡ ድርሰት፡</foreign> , with a drawing which relates to the prayer.
                    Incipit: <foreign xml:lang="gez">መሐልየ፡ መልያል፡ እብኖዲ፡ አብኖድያል፡ ሐራ፡ ሐራፑናዊ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ይቀጽብ፡ በኅቡዕ፡ ተኃባዕ፡ ውስተ፡ ልብየ፡ ማስያስ፡ ተፈታሕ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ከማሁ፡ አርእየኒ፡ ምሥጢረ፡ ድርሰት፡ ለገብርከ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></foreign>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a2">
                    <desc type="GuestText">
                    <locus target="#126r"/>, lines 3ff.: an extensive version of the concluding prayer for the <title type="complete" ref="LIT2701Dawit"/>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
