                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e4">
                    <desc>
                    Navigation system:
                    red string is sewn into the fore edge of <locus target="#20 #29 #36 #41 #48 #56 #67 #86 #89"/>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e5">
                    <desc>
                    Numbered quires: quires 2–5
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e6">
                    <desc>
                    Psalm 118 contains the spiritual meanings of the Hebrew letters
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e7">
                    <desc>
                    Scribal intervention:
                    words of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#2v #4v #5r #7v #10r"/>, etc.);
                    and lines of text are written interlinearly (<locus target="#2r #4r #26r #28v #34r"/>, etc.);
                    and in the upper margin with a symbol (+) marking the location where the text is to be inserted (<locus target="#12v"/>, line 18; <locus target="#14v"/>, line 9; <locus target="#21v"/>, line 1), and in another case where the symbol (┴) is used (<locus target="#91r"/>, line 1; <locus target="#102v"/>, line 2);
                    text has been removed (<locus target="#1r #32r #76r #82v #91v"/>, etc.).
                    </desc>
                    </item>

